{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-situations-page-tsx","path":"/en/situations/current-events-christmas/midnight-mass","result":{"data":{"situation":{"title":"Midnight Mass","meta_description":"Konání půlnoční v době pandemie. ","content":{"processed":"<h2>Rules and recommendations</h2>\n<p>Midnight masses are allowed to happen under specific hygiene rules. </p>\n<p>Only<strong> 20 % of the seating capacity may be occupied. </strong></p>\n<p>It is obligatory to <strong>keep a 2-meter distance</strong> <strong>from others</strong> people living in the same household are exempt from this rule. Upon entering the indoor premises of the church you must <strong>disinfect your hands. </strong></p>\n<p>During the sign of peace, no handshakes may occur. </p>\n<p>The general obligation to wear a mask applies. </p>\n<p>The rule of a maximum of 5 people singing together indoors applies. </p>\n<p>Singing together is prohibited. The singers or the choir must be in separate space. In that case, they must follow all the rules regarding mainly the minimum area per performer.</p>\n<p> </p>\n"},"path":{"alias":"/situations/current-events-christmas/midnight-mass"},"changed":"2020-12-23T18:51:03+00:00","valid_from":"2020-12-23T00:00:00+01:00","langcode":"en","created":"2020-12-23T18:51:03+00:00","links":[],"relationships":{"region":[{"name":"All regions of Czechia"}],"icon":null,"situation_type":{"name":"CURRENT EVENTS: Christmas","path":{"alias":"/situations/current-events-christmas"},"relationships":{"icon":{"code":"calendar_today"}}},"measures":[],"related_situations":[{"title":"Services and religious gatherings ","path":{"alias":"/situations/churches-and-religious-activities/services-and-religious-gatherings","langcode":"en"}},{"title":"Measures on free movement","path":{"alias":"/situations/free-movement-people/measures-free-movement","langcode":"en"}}]},"questions_answers":[],"update":null,"valid_to":null,"last_updated":"2020-12-23T16:23:34+01:00"},"situationArea":{"